p-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">4</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">流动人口数据分析</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>●来源分布</strong></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824404008472576.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824404444680192.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824404495011840.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>●文化层次</strong></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.noslink.com/editor/657824664676077568.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824663367454720.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824663430369280.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>●从事行业</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://www.noslink.com/editor/657824998253268992.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://www.noslink.com/editor/657824998186160128.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"/></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657824998211325952.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>●年龄结构</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://www.noslink.com/editor/657825395479023616.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://www.noslink.com/editor/657825395365777408.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"/></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"/editor/657825394875043840.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: right; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">数据统计时间：2015年10月</span><br/></p><hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"/><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"38806\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\"><section style=\"border-bottom-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 8px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgb(15, 95, 145); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: -5px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); color: rgb(30, 155, 232); font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); color: inherit;\">三、机构简介</strong></span></p></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85626\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"float: left; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-width: 35px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">1</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">机构沿革</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">福田区流动人口和出租屋综合管理办公室成立于2004年9月，与1989年设立的福田区房屋租赁管理局合署办公。2014年7月，按照全市的统一部署，设立福田区社区网格管理办公室，实行三块牌子一套人马的管理架构，参公管理编制。与此相应在十个街道设立流动人口和出租屋综合管理所、房屋租赁管理所、社区网格中心,为全额拨款事业编制。<br/></p><hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"/><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85626\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"float: left; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-width: 35px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">2</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">职能职责</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">1、贯彻执行国家、省、市关于出租屋管理的法律、法规和政策，并结合实际制定相应管理制度和办法；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2、依照“三定”方案，依法承担对全区房屋租赁的各项行政管理工作；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">3、根据房屋租赁当事人的申请，调解、处理房屋租赁纠纷；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">4、依法受理对违法租赁行为和违法管理行为的投诉，调查处理房屋租赁违法案件；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">5、依据房屋租赁市场价格水平，定期调查、核定、上报本区房屋租赁指导租金；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">6、负责全区房屋租赁管理及综合治理情况的统计上报工作；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">7、负责组织、指导、监督本区房屋租赁管理费的收取工作；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">8、协助相关职能部门，对出租屋实施社会综合治理；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">9、负责全区房屋租赁人员的法规及业务培训工作；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">10、负责全区房屋租赁法规、政策咨询和信访工作；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">11、负责房屋租赁行政诉讼案件应诉和行政处罚的调查取证工作；&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">12、法律、法规规定或区人民政府授予的其他职责。</p><hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"/><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85626\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"float: left; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-width: 35px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">3</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">领导分工</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit;\">廖吉安&nbsp;主任（局长），主持办（局）全面工作。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">黄远康&nbsp; 副主任（副局长），分管网格管理科和信息中心，负责网格管理、出租屋综管、信息维护、安全维稳等工作。协调福田、福保两个街道办事处，负责对相应街道综管所（租赁所）进行业务指导。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">林 峰&nbsp; 副主任（副局长），分管业务科，负责房屋租赁管理、租赁税代征工作。协调园岭、梅林、华富三个街道办事处，负责对相应街道综管所（租赁所）进行业务指导。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">郑增强&nbsp; 副主任（副局长），分管稽查科，负责行政执法审批工作。协调沙头、香蜜湖、莲花三个街道办事处，负责对相应街道综管所（租赁所）进行业务指导。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">唐玉宏&nbsp; 副主任（副局长），负责人事、财务、行政审批和党群、信访、培训、电子政务、会议会务、提案议案、制度建设、党风廉政建设和作风行风建设等工作。协调南园、华强北两个街道办事处，负责对相应街道综管所（租赁所）进行业务指导。则，机关各科室对分管领导所挂街道综管所（租赁所）及社区进行业务指导。</p><hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"/><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85626\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"float: left; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-width: 35px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">4</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">支部建设</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit;\">成立区综管办（租赁局）党支部，支部现有党员17名。廖吉安同志任支部书记，唐玉宏同志任支部副书记，陈思华同志为组织纪检委员。</span></p><hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"/><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85626\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"float: left; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-top-width: 35px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-left-width: 14px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; border-right-width: 14px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -30px; margin-left: -5px; color: inherit; line-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><strong style=\"color:inherit\"><em class=\"autonum\" style=\"color: inherit;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">5</em></strong></span></section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 36px; color: rgb(117, 117, 118); border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">队伍配备</span></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/editor/657853986031931392.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"队伍配备.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p></section>', '2015-10-25 09:35:44', '1', '1');
INSERT INTO `wg_introduction` VALUES ('8', '<section class=\"article135\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"62942\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"white-space: normal; font-family: sans-serif; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"width: 100%; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232) rgb(198, 198, 198) rgb(198, 198, 198); border-style: solid; border-width: 8px 1px 1px; padding: 15px 10px 5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-style=\"text-align: center; line-height:2em;\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85616\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"layout\" data-width=\"95%\" style=\"width: 95%; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"padding: 10px; line-height: 2em; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(89, 150, 235); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><strong><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“福田综管”微信平台用户手册</span></strong></section><p><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibFa8hbzHetsNTXuYCBmRffsYZ8PRWZtwBxfyibqc9iaXu1bJLt4NAtw2NIxWNJ4GoKakhs0Qlyz3MMw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p></section></section><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">基本概况</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">基本概况用于展示综管办相关职能以及机构信息介绍，面向公众，让用户进一步了解机构，更好的提供服务。</p><p><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">资讯发布</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">资讯发布包含三部分内容: 1、政务资讯；2、业务手册；3、政策法规。管理员通过公众号管理系统中的资讯发布模块发布政务资讯、法律法规、业务手册等相关信息资讯内容在当前模块。用户可选择某条资讯点击浏览。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">员工风采</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">员工风采用于展示综管办优秀的员工楷模，表扬在工作中取得优秀成果的职员，展现良好的风貌，传递正能量。可通过后台系统设置展示的人员资料。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">咨询服务</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">咨询服务模块包含在线咨询，意见与建议，办事机构等三个部分。提供在线提问答疑，进一步加强工作人员与群众的互动交流，及时提供帮助，解决问题，提高工作效率。同时群众可通过意见与建议将发现的问题反馈给工作人员。此外在办事机构部分提供了综管办相关的地址以及联系方式，方便与群众沟通互动。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息快采</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>1、功能描述:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">任意系统用户发现可疑或危险事件可能发生或正在发生、或有其它重大事件时，用户通过拍照，拍视频的方式将事件记录，加上事件的详细描述，事件发生的地址等详细信息录入到如图中的界面上及时报给上级机构。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>2、操作步骤:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;有重大事件发生:当存在发生事件时，保持当前开关为绿色状态；若无事件上报，则点击开关，上报无重大事件报告。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;即将或可能发生的重特大信息:事件还未发生，则点击选择该项目，如果事件正在发生，则选择已经或正在发生的重特大信息。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;专项行动重特大信息:如果当前处于专项行动期间,则所上报的重特大信息将会自动归于本次专项行动。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;照片上传:将拍照保留的事件现场照片点击上传至此处，有图有真相，图片可以上传多张。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;事件发生的地址:手机通过GPS定位当前位置，当页面弹出是否允许获取当前位置时,此处必须点击允许系统才能自动获取当前位置信息，还可以进行修订成为更加准确的地址信息。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;事件详细描述:&nbsp;将发现的事件，用准确的文字描述清晰。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;上述步骤完成后点击上报按钮即可完成此次快报作业。此时您上报的信息将发往上一级单位。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;上传视频（可选）:当有必要传送视频内容时，在以上操作完成后,回到公众号菜单入口界面如图，在10分钟内进行小视频录制并发送至公众号，此视频将会添加到快报作业。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;查看上报记录:点击可查看上报历史记录，历史记录会将您所有的上报记录全部列出来，您可以选中历史记录进行编辑，追加照片、视频、修改事件发生的地址和详细描述等。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息快报</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">信息快报是社区、街道和区办等各级部门逐级进行重特大事件的上报界面。每个层级的工作人员、负责人都只能看到本单位的信息。其中&quot;接收信息&quot;是指从下级单位上报上来的重特大信息。本单位专职人员可以从接收信息列表中选择需要进行上报的重特大事件，并且按&quot;确认&quot;按钮即可筛选至&quot;上报信息&quot;。本单位负责人才有权限将筛选出来的事件上报上级单位。本单位的其他工作人员不参与筛选及上报工作，但可以进行查看和评论。比如：</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;网格员上报信息后，社区工作人员可在接收信息处查看到收到的事件记录;</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;社区专职人员根据过滤选取接收信息至上报信息，还可以将无需上报的事件退回。社区负责人将上报信息中的信息选择性上报至街道。如果事件无需上报，负责人可将事件舍弃，退回及舍弃的事件都会被删除，但可以在右下角（当有事件被删除才显示）的垃圾桶内找回。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;街道专职人员收到社区上报的事件后,过滤选取接收信息至上报信息,流程同步骤2。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;相关工作人员可以进行查看及对此事件进行快速评论和领导批示。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">我要点评</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">点击菜单进入我要点评界面,在此可查看到上报的事件记录以及评论数,点击&quot;我要点评&quot;直接进入评论页面（如图），可从模板中选择评论语或输入评论，点击&quot;确定&quot;评论完成。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">互联互通</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:&nbsp;互联互通中根据用户查看权限显示市、区领导、区职能部门和各个街道办事处负责人的联系方式，如果有权限，则可根据部门结构找到对应的联系人后拨打，若权限不够则不能拨打。(注:灰色表示无拨打电话权限，蓝色表示有拨打电话权限)</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息查询</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:各个单位的工作人员都可以在信息查询中输入各种查询条件过滤,查找到本单位及管辖的区域所发生的重特大事件信息记录。比如街道相关工作人员只能看到本街道辖区内的事件记录，还可以选择下一级社区查找社区的事件记录。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">数据统计</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:用户查看统计数据受权限约束,可按起止时间，部门机构以及事件类别、时间段、关键字、采集人、采集区域、采集人（积分）,采集区域(积分)、专项行动等9类查询条件统计上报事件。各个单位的工作人员只能查看到本单位及管辖的区域所发生的重特大事件数据统计。比如街道相关工作人员只能看到本街道辖区内的事件数据统计，还可以选择下一级社区查看社区的事件数据统计。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">作风建设</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:根据用户权限搜索对应的用户，可查看用户活动路径。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">平台指引</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:1、操作手册,用户根据手册的指导说明，使用当前公众号平台。2、业务规范，介绍综管办的机制与业务流程内容;3、用户中心，查看当前用户，修改密码解除绑定。</p></section></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p></section>', '2015-10-25 22:07:04', '1', '2');
INSERT INTO `wg_introduction` VALUES ('9', '绑定用户说明', '2015-10-10 02:30:11', '1', '3');
INSERT INTO `wg_introduction` VALUES ('10', '<section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"62942\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"white-space: normal; border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"width: 100%; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232) rgb(198, 198, 198) rgb(198, 198, 198); border-style: solid; border-width: 8px 1px 1px; padding: 15px 10px 5px; text-align: center;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-style=\"text-align: center; line-height:2em;\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 5px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85616\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"width:100%;margin:0 auto;\" data-width=\"100%\"><section style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; background-color: rgb(89, 150, 235);\"><strong><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“福田综管”微信平台用户手册</span></strong></section><p style=\"margin-top:0px;\"><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibFa8hbzHetsNTXuYCBmRffsYZ8PRWZtwBxfyibqc9iaXu1bJLt4NAtw2NIxWNJ4GoKakhs0Qlyz3MMw/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"height:auto !important; width:100%\" data-width=\"100%\"/></p></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">管理概况</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">基本概况用于展示综管办相关职能以及机构信息介绍，面向公众，让用户进一步了解机构，更好的提供服务。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">资讯发布</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">资讯发布包含三部分内容: 1、政务资讯；2、业务手册；3、政策法规。管理员通过公众号管理系统中的资讯发布模块发布政务资讯、法律法规、业务手册等相关信息资讯内容在当前模块。用户可选择某条资讯点击浏览。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">员工风采</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">员工风采用于展示综管办优秀的员工楷模，表扬在工作中取得优秀成果的职员，展现良好的风貌，传递正能量。可通过后台系统设置展示的人员资料。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" data-custom=\"rgb(30, 155, 232)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(30, 155, 232); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">一、信息资讯</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(30, 155, 232); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">咨询服务</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">咨询服务模块包含在线咨询，意见与建议，办事机构等三个部分。提供在线提问答疑，进一步加强工作人员与群众的互动交流，及时提供帮助，解决问题，提高工作效率。同时群众可通过意见与建议将发现的问题反馈给工作人员。此外在办事机构部分提供了综管办相关的地址以及联系方式，方便与群众沟通互动。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息快采</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>1、功能描述:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">任意系统用户发现可疑或危险事件可能发生或正在发生、或有其它重大事件时，用户通过拍照，拍视频的方式将事件记录，加上事件的详细描述，事件发生的地址等详细信息录入到如图中的界面上及时报给上级机构。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>2、操作步骤:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;有重大事件发生:当存在发生事件时，保持当前开关为绿色状态；若无事件上报，则点击开关，上报无重大事件报告。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;即将或可能发生的重特大信息:事件还未发生，则点击选择该项目，如果事件正在发生，则选择已经或正在发生的重特大信息。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;专项行动重特大信息:如果当前处于专项行动期间,则所上报的重特大信息将会自动归于本次专项行动。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;照片上传:将拍照保留的事件现场照片点击上传至此处，有图有真相，图片可以上传多张。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;事件发生的地址:手机通过GPS定位当前位置，当页面弹出是否允许获取当前位置时,此处必须点击允许系统才能自动获取当前位置信息，还可以进行修订成为更加准确的地址信息。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;事件详细描述: 将发现的事件，用准确的文字描述清晰。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;上述步骤完成后点击上报按钮即可完成此次快报作业。此时您上报的信息将发往上一级单位。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;上传视频（可选）:当有必要传送视频内容时，在以上操作完成后,回到公众号菜单入口界面如图，在10分钟内进行小视频录制并发送至公众号，此视频将会添加到快报作业。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;查看上报记录:点击可查看上报历史记录，历史记录会将您所有的上报记录全部列出来，您可以选中历史记录进行编辑，追加照片、视频、修改事件发生的地址和详细描述等。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息快报</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">信息快报是社区、街道和区办等各级部门逐级进行重特大事件的上报界面。每个层级的工作人员、负责人都只能看到本单位的信息。其中”接收信息”是指从下级单位上报上来的重特大信息。本单位专职人员可以从接收信息列表中选择需要进行上报的重特大事件，并且按”确认”按钮即可筛选至”上报信息”。本单位负责人才有权限将筛选出来的事件上报上级单位。本单位的其他工作人员不参与筛选及上报工作，但可以进行查看和评论。比如：<br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;网格员上报信息后，社区工作人员可在接收信息处查看到收到的事件记录;</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;社区专职人员根据过滤选取接收信息至上报信息，还可以将无需上报的事件退回。社区负责人将上报信息中的信息选择性上报至街道。如果事件无需上报，负责人可将将事件舍弃，退回及舍弃的事件都会被删除，但您可以在右下角（当有事件被删除才显示）的垃圾桶内找回。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;街道专职人员收到社区上报的事件后,过滤选取接收信息至上报信息,流程同步骤2。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">◆&nbsp;相关工作人员可以进行查看及对此事件进行快速评论和领导批示。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">我要点评</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">点击菜单进入我要点评界面,在此刻查看到上报的事件记录以及评论数,点击我要点评直接进入评论页面如图，可从模板中选择评论语或输入评论，点击确定评论完成。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" data-custom=\"rgb(128, 177, 53)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">二、快采快报</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(128, 177, 53); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">互联互通</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述: 互联互通中根据用户查看权限显示市、区领导、区职能部门和各个街道办事处负责人的联系方式，如果有权限则，可根据部门结构找到对应的联系人后拨打，若权限不够则不能拨打。(注:灰色表示无拨打电话权限，蓝色表示有拨打电话权限)</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">信息查询</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:各个单位的工作人员都可以在信息查询中输入各种查询条件过滤,查找到本单位及管辖的区域所发生的重特大事件信息记录。比如街道相关工作人员只能看到本街道辖区内的事件记录，还可以选择下一级社区查找社区的事件记录。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">数据统计</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:用户查看统计数据受权限约束,可按起止时间，部门机构以及事件类别、时间段、关键字、采集人、采集区域、采集人（积分）,采集区域(积分)、专项行动等9类查询条件统计上报事件。各个单位的工作人员只能查看到本单位及管辖的区域所发生的重特大事件数据统计。比如街道相关工作人员只能看到本街道辖区内的事件数据统计，还可以选择下一级社区查看社区的事件数据统计。统计结果如下图:</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">作风建设</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:根据用户权限搜索对应的用户，可查看用户活动路径。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"82867\" data-color=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" data-custom=\"rgb(239, 112, 96)\" style=\"border: 0px none; padding: 0px;\"><section style=\"clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><section style=\"font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"border: 0px rgb(239, 112, 96); margin-top: 2px; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">三、管理支持</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 20px 32px 0px; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(239, 112, 96); z-index: 3; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"height: 32px; -webkit-transform: skew(32deg); display: inline-block; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-width: 10px; border-right-style: solid; color: inherit;\"><section data-bclessp=\"8%\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: inherit;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-transform: skew(-32deg); color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 8px 15px; display: inline-block;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">平台指引</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">功能描述:1、操作手册,用户根据手册的指导说明，使用当前公众号平台。2、业务规范，介绍综管办的机制与业务流程内容;3、用户中心，查看当前用户，修改密码解除绑定。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p>', '2015-10-25 15:20:31', '1', '4');

