border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"90%\" width=\"90%\" height=\"auto\" border=\"0\" opacity=\"\" mapurl=\"\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><br/></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\"><section style=\"margin: 4px 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">赵彬</span></strong></span>（华富街道梅岗社区网格员）</p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">9月30日，华富街道梅岗社区网格员赵彬，在园林宿舍3栋核实、登记实有人口信息时，发现303号人员混居现象严重，煤气炉多，电线随意乱拉，为防患于未然，赵彬对303号人员进行了训导，令其整改，消除安全隐患，并将信息及时上报。赵彬这种细致的观察力值得每一个网格员学习。</span></p><section style=\"width: 100%; border-width: 2px 0px 8px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin-top: 15px; padding: 2px; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; height: 12px; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\" data-width=\"100%\"></section></section></section><section style=\"width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\"></section></section><p><br/></p>', '1', '网格员');
